:\n*: White Hmong: {{tt|mww|nceb}}\n* Hungarian: {{tt+|hu|gomba}}, {{tt+|hu|termőtest}}\n* Icelandic: {{tt+|is|sveppur|m}}\n* Ido: {{tt+|io|fungo}}\n* Ilocano: {{tt|ilo|uong}}\n* Indonesian: {{tt+|id|jamur}}\n* Ingrian: {{tt|izh|opokka}}, {{tt|izh|griba}}, {{tt|izh|seeni}}\n* Inupiaq: {{tt|ik|argaiġñaq}}\n* Irish: {{tt|ga|beacán|m}}, {{tt|ga|muisiriún|m}}\n* Italian: {{tt+|it|fungo|m}}\n* Japanese: {{tt+|ja|キノコ|tr=kinoko}}, {{tt+|ja|茸|tr=kinoko}}, {{tt+|ja|きのこ|tr=kinoko}}\n* Javanese: {{tt+|jv|jamur}}\n* Kalmyk: {{tt|xal|теңгрин ки}}\n* Kanakanabu: {{t|xnb|tavununga}}\n* Kannada: {{tt+|kn|ನಾಯಿಕೊಡೆ}}, {{tt+|kn|ಅಣಬೆ}}\n* Kapampangan: {{tt|pam|kabuti}}, {{tt|pam|payungdagis}}, {{tt|pam|payung-payungan}}\n* Karachay-Balkar: {{tt|krc|жууа|tr=juwa}}, {{tt|krc|джууа|tr=cuwa}}, {{tt|krc|тошлакъ}}\n* Karakalpak: {{tt|kaa|zamarrıq}}, {{tt|kaa|qozıqulaq}}\n* Karelian: {{tt|krl|sieni}}\n* Karen:\n*: S'gaw Karen: {{tt|ksw|ကုၤ}}\n* Kashubian: {{tt|csb|grzib|m}}\n* Kazakh: {{tt|kk|саңырауқұлақ}}, {{tt|kk|қозықұйрық}}\n* Ket: {{tt|ket|больба}}\n* Khakas: {{tt|kjh|миске}}\n* Khmer: {{tt+|km|ផ្សិត}}\n* Komi:\n*: Komi-Zyrian: {{tt|kpv|тшак}}\n* Kongo: {{tt|kg|luwa}}\n* Korean: {{tt+|ko|버섯}}\n* Kumyk: {{tt|kum|къолкъотур}}\n* Kurdish:\n*: Central Kurdish: {{tt|ckb|قارچک}}, {{tt|ckb|کوارگ}}\n*: Northern Kurdish: {{tt+|kmr|kuvark}}, {{tt+|kmr|kavkulîlk}}\n* Kyrgyz: {{tt+|ky|козу карын}}\n* Lakota: {{tt|lkt|čhaŋnákpa}}\n* Lao: {{tt+|lo|ກະດ້າງ}}, {{tt|lo|ເຫັດ}}\n* Latgalian: {{tt|ltg|sieņs|f}}\n* Latin: {{tt|la|fungus|m}}, {{tt|la|bōlētus|m}}\n* Latvian: {{tt+|lv|sēne|f}}\n* Lingala: {{tt|ln|likombó|c5|c6}}\n* Lithuanian: {{tt+|lt|grybas|m}}\n* Lombard: {{tt|lmo|fung}}, {{tt|lmo|fungg}}\n* Low German: {{tt|nds|Paddenstohl|m}}, {{tt|nds|Poggenstohl|m}}, {{tt|nds|Swamm|m}}\n* Lushootseed: {{t|lut|šapiyu}}\n* Macedonian: {{tt+|mk|печурка|f}}\n* Malagasy: {{tt+|mg|holatra}}\n* Malay: {{tt+|ms|cendawan}}\n*: Brunei Malay: {{tt|kxd|kulat}}\n* Malayalam: {{tt+|ml|കുമിൾ}}, {{tt+|ml|കൂൺ}}\n* Maltes